attributes.action: Seek to form a free movement union and passport across CANZUK
attributes.additional_details: We believe this proposal would strengthen political, economic and cultural ties, particularly as the USA grows into what we believe is an increasingly unreliable ally; fostering deeper cooperation, unity, and mutual opportunity across all four countries.
attributes.background: We urge the UK Government to seek to negotiate a CANZUK Union passport with Canada, Australia and New Zealand to ensure free movement across the four nations. As key Anglosphere nations with shared heritage, we believe it would let citizens live, work and travel freely, while strengthening ties.
